<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/login-page.css"/>
    <title>Login</title>

</head>
<body>

<!-- 상단 바 -->
<div class="topbar">
    <button class="btn" onclick="location.href='/'">Logo Area</button>
    <button class="btn primary" onclick="location.href='/join'">JoinBtn Area</button>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <div class="grid">
        <!-- Left: 소개 -->
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>Lorem Ipsum</h1>
            <p>
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Viverra id lacinia nisl fringilla eget a.
                Est habitasse mattis penatibus turpis feugiat. Eget sed nibh dui proin leo amet
                etiam. At neque quisque sed nunc tempor. Risus hendrerit egestas sit est nisl blandit morbi.
                Arcu leo et leo nunc purus aliquam mollis ut justo. At aliquam elit egestas eget mi imperdiet in in
                magna.
                Pellentesque vitae lacus at suspendisse commodo gravida duis massa nulla. Risus est arcu placerat
                lobortis risus sed cras.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Right: 폼 -->
        <section class="panel">
            <h3>로그인</h3>
            <form method="post" action="/login">
                <!-- 서버에서 CSRF 토큰을 내려주면 바인딩 -->
                {{#_csrf}}
                    <input type="hidden" name="{{parameterName}}" value="{{token}}">
                {{/_csrf}}

                <input class="field" type="text" name="username" placeholder="아이디" value="{{prefillUsername}}">
                <input class="field" type="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호">

                <button class="btn primary submit" type="submit">LogIn</button>

                <div class="helper">
                    <a href="/join">회원가입</a>
                </div>
            </form>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="footerline"></div>

</body>
</html>
